	<div style="position: relative; float: left; width: 510px;">Magelo Sync is a quick and easy way to synchronize your character and create your profile, signature and avatar but it goes beyond that. Thanks to its related section and its quick search the Magelo database stay in touch whenever you need it. Stay connected!  </div>
	<div style="position:relative;float: left; left:40px; top:-2px;" >
<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/shared/buttons/magelo_sync_off.png?v=12500" height="56" width="230" />		<div style="position:absolute; top:17px; left:56px; font-weight: bold;">Download&nbsp;Magelo&nbsp;Sync</div>
